100
00:05:06,386 --> 00:05:08,668
Oh, look! There he is right now.

101
00:05:08,668 --> 00:05:11,438
Maybe he'll help us.

102
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,920
He'll help us.

103
00:05:13,969 --> 00:05:16,158
Gilbert: You know, we've always
talked about wanting to do,

104
00:05:16,158 --> 00:05:18,686
you know, more classic adventure stuff.

105
00:05:18,686 --> 00:05:20,752
And so doing the
Kickstarter thing, it's like,

106
00:05:20,752 --> 00:05:24,665
yeah, that sounds, I mean, that
sounds really like an interesting idea.

107
00:05:24,665 --> 00:05:29,210
I think we were both very
skeptical about the amount of money.

108
00:05:29,210 --> 00:05:32,354
Schafer: So, we are asking for
