people and lift them up a bit.

180
00:08:34,046 --> 00:08:38,197
Young Man: Because Tim Schafer
has consistently put out quality games.

181
00:08:38,197 --> 00:08:42,296
Man: Games that have very
large and dedicated followings.

182
00:08:42,296 --> 00:08:46,303
Man: People would probably pay
