193
00:09:17,006 --> 00:09:20,078
We've never laid off
anyone for money before.

194
00:09:20,078 --> 00:09:24,424
So we were, and even besides
the financial concerns, it was just such a,

195
00:09:24,424 --> 00:09:26,772
it doesn't feel like you're winning
when you have a game canceled.

196
00:09:26,772 --> 00:09:30,532
You feel like it's a big,
you know, you've lost.

197
00:09:30,532 --> 00:09:33,677
Schafer: I'm about to launch
our first Kickstarter project.

198
00:09:33,677 --> 00:09:36,606
Rice: It kind of just all came together
