00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:12,860
Are you guys ok? What happened?

258
00:12:14,610 --> 00:12:16,677
Oh, they're being
crushed. It's horrible.

259
00:12:16,677 --> 00:12:19,737
Muir: Oh, no! No!

260
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:22,480
What happened?

261
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,620
[Distortion]

