00:16:57,974 --> 00:17:01,272
pessimistic brain that says, well,
you can never do this again.

360
00:17:01,272 --> 00:17:06,079
That this was really kind of this
one time perfect storm thing.

361
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:10,114
But I don't know. I mean, maybe not.

362
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:22,359
[Music]

363
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:31,520
[Cheering]

364
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:33,879
I've been so happy about that

