00:17:33,879 --> 00:17:35,515
ever since Kickstarter started,

366
00:17:35,515 --> 00:17:37,672
just thinking about how, I
still have to answer to people.

367
00:17:37,672 --> 00:17:39,646
Like people funded the game, you know.

368
00:17:39,646 --> 00:17:41,827
But they're exactly the
people I want to answer to.

369
00:17:41,827 --> 00:17:43,864
Those are the people
I'm making dots for, right?

370
00:17:43,864 --> 00:17:46,197
And all those things
like, and so it's like,

371
00:17:46,197 --> 00:17:50,544
it's just this really liberating,

372
00:17:50,544 --> 00:17:52,455
freeing thing to just
think that I'm just going to

373
00:17:52,455 --> 00:17:54,615
have to worry about how good
the game is, almost nothing else.

374
00:17:54,820 --> 00:18:04,080
[Music]

