00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:05,240
Schafer: I love you guys!

376
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:08,599
It has been an amazing
experience. So much love.

377
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:11,004
We know there's not, it's not
all about us and Double Fine,

378
00:18:11,004 --> 00:18:13,747
but about you, the fans and
what you guys want to say

379
00:18:13,747 --> 00:18:15,939
and do with your money and choose to do.

380
00:18:15,939 --> 00:18:18,375
And make things happen for yourself.

381
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:21,150
I mean, I don't want to
make a huge speech here,

382
00:18:21,150 --> 00:18:22,785
because I'll be all choked up.

383
00:18:22,785 --> 00:18:24,779
Gilbert: Too late.

384
00:18:24,779 --> 00:18:27,431
Schafer: But I just, I don't
want to say this is the end of the,

