386
00:18:29,837 --> 00:18:32,857
It's not, it's not.

387
00:18:32,857 --> 00:18:35,511
And it's not, again it's not
like we're total replacement

388
00:18:35,511 --> 00:18:37,824
of all publishers and publishing games.

